+## [0.2.6] - 2026-05-27
+
+Internal utility & tooling release. Three dependency-free helper modules under
+`src/lib`, a `node --test` harness, and the ADR/planning docs. Non-breaking; no
+behavioral change to shipped routes.
+
+> Post-reset version reconciliation: this workspace's prior release tags
+> `v0.2.1`–`v0.2.5` point to commits orphaned by repeated resets (HEAD was at
+> `0.2.0`). Per the no-overwrite / tag-conflict rules, this release increments
+> past the burned numbers to `0.2.6` rather than colliding.
+
+### Added
+
+- `src/lib/slug.ts` — `slugify()` URL-safe slug helper (ADR-0002).
+- `src/lib/num.ts` — `clamp()` and `roundTo()` numeric helpers (ADR-0002).
+- `src/lib/str.ts` — `truncate()` and `titleCase()` string helpers (ADR-0002).
+- `npm test` harness (`node --import tsx --test`) + `tsx` devDependency, with
+  co-located unit tests (24 tests passing).
+- ADR-0001 (test-harness & pure-logic coverage), ADR-0002 (parallel pure-utility
+  modules), backlog brainstorm (Markdown + JSON), and the moonshots-2026-05-21
+  planning set.
+
+### Changed
+
+- README tech-stack refreshed to the 0.2.0 platform (Next.js 16 · React 19 ·
+  TypeScript 6 · Tailwind CSS 4 · ESLint 10).
+
